room_title: Escape room "The Classroom" by All Locked Up in Los Angeles
room_address: 18914 Soledad Canyon Rd Santa Clarita, CA 91351
room_description: It's Summer school and you need to help your friend get 100% on their Summer School Test to pass the class and make it into the next grade. Your job is to make sure that they make the grade. Scott has to help his friend get the grade they need to succeed in school. Making things easier, there was an accident on the road so some of the teachers are running late, thus buying you some time to get in and out with the answers to the final test. Good Luck!
